# This file is intentionally not used by edgeclaw-opc.
#
# Configure the repository root instead:
#   cp ../.env.example ../.env
#
# The repository root .env is the only user-facing config entry. It also holds
# gateway-related variables. claude-code-main/start.sh and proxy.ts derive their
# internal OPENAI_* / ANTHROPIC_* runtime variables from EDGECLAW_*.
